    </p>

    <p>
      Choose this setup if you would like to extend and customize the library to your needs.
    </p>

    {{#code 'bash'}}
npm install @bpmn-io/form-js
    {{/code}}

    <p>
      <strong>Note:</strong> This requires additional build steps such as bundling for the browser with <a href="http://browserify.org/">Browserify</a> or <a href="https://webpack.github.io/">Webpack</a>.
